title: Blimps
description:
In Blimps, produced by Topper Studios, you must survive the war by shooting down hostile blimps. There are multiple kinds of ammunition, and many different kinds of blimps, some tougher than others, some more destructive than others.

This contains the app for iPhone/iPod touch [it requires a jailbroken device, of course] and the theme song. The app provided is identical to the full version.

If you enjoy the app or the theme song, please buy it from the App Store!
